data.text:
UNOBTAINABLE

This feature is unobtainable and can only be obtained via hacking.

JAPANESE EXCLUSIVE

This feature is exclusive to the Japanese version of The Battle Cats but it may also appear in other versions such as BCTW and BCKR!

For the Cat Unit, see Type 10 (Special Cat). Not to be confused with Type 10 (Event Enemy).

Type 10 was a Traitless enemy that appeared in the Hometown Self-Defense Force Collaboration Event.

Enemy[]

Type 10 was a tank with fairly low standing range, damage and movement speed.

Strategy[]

A very easy enemy to defeat, shouldn't have posed much of a threat due to its low range and other low stats. Any of the Normal Cats could make quick work of it.

Encounters[]

Trivia[]

This enemy was based on the Type 10 Main Battle Tank of the Japan Self-Defense Forces.

https://battlecats-db.com/enemy/057.html
